==Management==
[[Image:TSEliotFaberHouse.jpg|thumb|right|Outside the SOAS Faber Building, 24 [[Russell Square]], commemorating [[T. S. Eliot]]'s years at [[Faber and Faber]].]]
2006 - present
[[Paul Webley]] is the current Director and Principal of SOAS. He was previously Senior Deputy Vice Chancellor and Professor of [[economic psychology|Economic Psychology]] at the [[University of Exeter]].

2001-2006 
[[Colin Bundy]] spent five years as Director and Principal of SOAS (and three years as Deputy Vice-Chancellor of the [[University of London]]). In 2006, he accepted appointment as Warden of [[Green College, Oxford]].<ref name = "Oxford Blueprint">{{cite web
