*Graham Furniss, (obtained his first degree at SOAS) Current Pro-Director of SOAS, Professor of African Language Literature and a Fellow of the [[British Academy]]<ref>http://www.britac.ac.uk/fellowship/elections/furniss.cfm</ref>

